Wash and dry produce.

Trim, peel, and dice @carrots{6%ounce} into ¼-inch pieces. Remove strings from @sugar snap peas{4%ounce}; halve crosswise on a diagonal. Peel and mince or grate @ginger{1%thumb}. Peel and mince @garlic{1%clove}. Trim and thinly slice @scallions{2}, separating whites from greens.

== Sesame Soy Sauce ==

In a #small bowl{}, combine @sweet soy glaze{4%tablespoon}, half the @sesame oil{1%tablespoon}, half the @rice wine vinegar{5%teaspoon}, and @sugar{1%teaspoon}.

> For 4 servings, use all the sesame oil, all the vinegar, and 2 tsp sugar.

== Sriracha Mayo ==

In a separate small bowl, combine @mayonnaise{2%tablespoon} with @sriracha{1%teaspoon} to taste. Add water 1 tsp at a time until mixture reaches a drizzling consistency. Season with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

== Vegetable Stir-Fry ==

Heat a drizzle of @cooking oil{} in a #large pan{}, preferably nonstick, over medium-high heat. Add carrots; season with salt and pepper. Cook, stirring, until slightly tender, ~{4-5%minutes}.

Add snap peas and cook until slightly tender, ~{1-2%minutes}.

Add ginger, garlic, and scallion whites; cook until fragrant, ~{30-60%seconds}.

Stir in sesame soy mixture. Cook, stirring, until sauce has thickened and veggies are coated, ~{1-2%minutes} more. Turn off heat; transfer veggie mixture to a #large bowl{}. Wipe out pan.

== Fried Rice ==

Heat a drizzle of cooking oil in pan used for veggies over medium-high heat. Massage @microwaveable jasmine rice{1} in package to break up grains, then add to pan. Cook, without stirring, until slightly crispy on bottom, ~{2-3%minutes}.

Add veggie mixture and stir to combine.

Season with salt and pepper to taste. Press into an even layer; cook until rice is slightly crispy, ~{1-2%minutes} more. Turn off heat.

== Fried Eggs ==

Heat a drizzle of cooking oil in a #medium pan{}, preferably nonstick, (use a large pan for 4 servings) over medium-high heat. Once hot, crack @eggs{2} into pan and cover. Fry eggs to preference. Season with salt and pepper.

> For 4 servings, you may want to cook eggs in batches.

== To Serve ==

Divide veggie fried rice between #bowls{}; top each with a fried egg. Drizzle with Sriracha mayo, garnish with scallion greens, and serve.